name: Ticket to Too Cool for School Tour
description:
Will Call presale ticket to Too Cool for School Tour on Friday August 26th featuring Legacy and Ace Augustine with support from Handed to the Thousands (as seen at The Community Collisions Fest), A World Away, and Treason Among Thieves.

In the PayPal message, PLEASE put down your full name and a phone number we can contact you. Remember, this is Will Call so please bring your Driver's License or another form of ID with you when you go to the show.

For show information:

name: The Community Takeover Compilation
description:
Check out our first official Fans 4 Bands Compilation!
Featuring 20 of the best Hardcore/Metalcore acts across the country and beyond, this is the sampler of the year!

Featuring bands like: No Bragging Rights, Feed Her To The Sharks, In Oceans, In Alcatraz 1962 and Sirens & Sailors. There is undoubtedly something for everyone. 

Show your support to the next generation of artists leading our scene by picking up this compilation!

This Compilation is FREE with any purchase.

name: Fans 4 Bands T Shirt
description: Represent the cause you support by wearing a Fans 4 Bands T Shirt! This is the most beneficial way to help support TOUR SUPPORT! 100% of these proceeds go back to bands in our community.
